div.head: Description of changes for 2012.12
div.p: This is the first public version of this text. It is a first draft copied from the descriptive transcription of the St. Victor manuscript. A transcription of the Sorbonne transcription still needs to be completed. Corrections and additiongs will be made pending a collation comparision of available manuscript witnesses. Troublesome transciptions have been marked as unclear. Name refrence attributeshave been aded to name elements in the edited version. Citations, cross-refereences and a critical apparatus still await construction.
